data.title: Primary care networks: a marathon not a sprint
data.text:
TY - JOUR

T1 - Primary care networks: a marathon not a sprint

AU - Smith, Judith

AU - Harshfield, Amelia

PY - 2019/9/10

Y1 - 2019/9/10

N2 - Primary care networks must seek to under-promise, and over-deliver, to enable them to garner and sustain the support of their constituent staff and practices, put in place much-needed services for local people, and build an important and powerful evidence base for the future.
